                                                       // selected game, the number of results found, and the refresh button.\n\t* Below is 
                                                       // a panel with quick access icons and a menu button. All icons are duplicated on the 
                                                       // menu, so if you do not know the meaning of the icon, it can always be viewed by 
                                                       // clicking on the menu button (the rightmost).\n\t* Below those icons will be the 
                                                       // list of search results.\n\nSaved list tab contains:\n\t* Pause button, the name 
