    public static final int help_fuzzy_search = 0x7F070126;  // string:help_fuzzy_search "* Fuzzy search:\n\t1. Switch to __app_name__ from a game.\n\t2. 
                                                             // Tap the \"__search_unknown_value__\" button in the \"__search__\" tab.\n\t3. Select 
