    public static final int help_games_protection = 0x7F07026F;  // string:help_games_protection "\tSome games are equipped with protection against 
                                                                 // memory editors. You can try the following:\n\t1. \"__kill_game__\", and then \"__restart_game_without_protection__\".\n\t2. 
                                                                 // \"__disable_protection__\", and then run (or restart) the game.\n\t3. Use all or 
                                                                 // part of the items in \"__hide_from_game__\". All of them slow down the search.\n\t4. 
                                                                 // Search when the game is minimized.\n\t5. Search when the game is paused.\n\t6. Kill 
                                                                 // or pause some of the protective processes of the game, if the game has several processes.\n\t7. 
                                                                 // Use XPrivacy or similar tools to bypass protection.\n\t8. Use the modification of 
                                                                 // the game without protection.\n    "
